About Whalley Computer Associates
WCA is one of the largest independent technology providers in New England. WCA, at its core, is a computer reseller but has grown to become a leader in system design, large scale technology deployments, inventory management, OEM server appliances, product development, and much more. WCA employs 140 computer professionals in Southwick and Milford Massachusetts and is seeking team players with positive attitudes and plenty of drive. WCA is looking to add an entry-level Computer Programmer to our growing team.
Job Description:
Support, maintain and enhance our legacy in-house developed WCA Programs
Programs written in C
ACTIAN Btrieve transactional database used
Understand and program business systems that include:
Accounting
Order entry
Inventory control
Production
Reporting for all departments
Integration/Reporting with Vendors and Customers
Communicate with colleagues and end-users
Working on a small team under the direction of the Sr. Programmers
Full-time position located at Corporate Headquarters
Opportunity for Advancement
